Building Requirements
---------------------

 * Ant   1.6 and up (1.7 recommended)
 * Java  1.5 and up (1.6 recommended)

Checking Out
------------

$ mkdir dtf
$ cd dtf
$ git clone https://[your_name]@github.com/rlgomes/dtf.git

Building
--------

$ ant build

Running a Test
--------------

$ cd build/dtf/dist
$ ./ant.sh run_dtfx -Ddtf.xml.filename=tests/ut/arithmetic.xml
